  {
    "id": "TALK_VAMPIRE_HUNTER_LEADER_WHY_NO_VAMPIRES",
    "type": "talk_topic",
    "dynamic_line": [
      "It has happened so many times.  A new recruit thinks they can beat fire with fire and goes past the point of no return.  When it happens, they either become another vampire or a killer of hunters.\n\nFor everyone's sake, I won't let you go down that path no matter what I must do."
    ],
    "responses": [
      { "text": "Okay, I'll get cured.  <end_talking_bye>", "topic": "TALK_DONE" },
      {
        "text": "It won't happen to me, though.",
        "topic": "TALK_VAMPIRE_HUNTER_LEADER_ULTIMATUM",
        "opinion": { "trust": -1, "value": -1, "anger": 1 }
      },
      {
        "text": "I won't take the cure.  There's nothing you can do about it.",
        "topic": "TALK_DONE",
        "effect": [ "hostile", { "run_eocs": "EOC_VAMPIRE_HUNTERS_PERMA_HOSTILE" } ],
        "opinion": { "trust": -30, "value": -30, "anger": 30 }
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "id": "TALK_VAMPIRE_HUNTER_LEADER_ULTIMATUM",
    "type": "talk_topic",
    "dynamic_line": [
      "They all said that, but it happened to each of them.  I won't ask again.  If you refuse the cure, we will have no choice but to kill you."
    ],
    "responses": [
      { "text": "Okay, I'll get cured.  <end_talking_bye>", "topic": "TALK_DONE" },
      {
        "text": "I won't take the cure.  There's nothing you can do about it.",
        "topic": "TALK_DONE",
