    "type": "talk_topic",
    "dynamic_line": [
      "This vampire was a lesser one, as seen by their resistance to the sun and lack of proper lair.  One day you will attack the lairs of true vampires alongside some of our hunters, but first we must find where they truly hide.  For now, we can enjoy some peace of mind and you can ask Elsa and Blaine for spare things to help you like you helped us."
    ],
    "responses": [
      { "text": "Let's talk about something else.", "topic": "TALK_NONE" },
      { "text": "<end_talking_bye>", "topic": "TALK_DONE" }
    ]
  },
  {
    "id": "TALK_KILL_RENFIELD_GANG_COMPLETED",
    "type": "talk_topic",
    "dynamic_line": [
      "They were close to our base, yet they did not attack it.  They were either on another mission or awaiting reinforcements before their attack.  I hope it's the former, for this base is why we did not had to risk our lives in the cities for food.  If they force us to choose between facing a raid or becoming nomads, we might never recover from it.  For now, we're alive and well thanks in no small part to you."
    ],
    "responses": [
      { "text": "Let's talk about something else.", "topic": "TALK_NONE" },
      { "text": "<end_talking_bye>", "topic": "TALK_DONE" }
    ]
  },
  {
    "id": "TALK_KILL_RENFIELD_MONSTER_COMPLETED",
    "type": "talk_topic",
    "dynamic_line": [
      "Renfields like that are rare and usually stay close to their masters to protect them.  If they're being sent to attack enemies, their masters are desperate or have many of them at their service.  It doesn't bode well, but at least you're able to kill them."
    ],
    "responses": [
      { "text": "Let's talk about something else.", "topic": "TALK_NONE" },
      { "text": "<end_talking_bye>", "topic": "TALK_DONE" }
    ]
  },
  {
    "id": "TALK_KILL_OR_CURE_COMPLETED_KILL",
    "type": "talk_topic",
    "dynamic_line": [
      "Unfortunate, but necessary.  Some don't want to be cured.  Even if we could forcefully administer it, they would go and get infected again.  Thank you for killing a future monster."
    ],
    "responses": [
      { "text": "Let's talk about something else.", "topic": "TALK_NONE" },
      { "text": "<end_talking_bye>", "topic": "TALK_DONE" }
    ]
  },
